Notes: Lord Jason is a member of the Heart & Soul server who had some issues with the auto note-taking bot, Merly. Lord Jason showed an interest in MBTI and questioned its validity, especially with respect to its ability to measure an individual's personality. He also displayed an interest in cringe and why fairies consider cringe a positive attribute.

Bio: Lord Jason is a curious and intelligent individual who enjoys deep conversations about complex topics like personality theory and existentialism. He also has a creative side that is reflected in his love for folklore and magic. His inquisitive nature and willingness to challenge preconceived notions suggest he is someone who seeks truth and understanding.

MBTI: INTP

Cringe-rating: 8/10
